The message of condolence of the Leader of the Islamic Revolution Ayatollah Seyyed Ali Khamenei was conveyed to the families of the martyrs of the recent terrorist attacks in Afghanistan. The Deputy Ambassador of the Islamic Republic of Iran in Kabul and the accompanying delegation met with the families of the martyrs of the recent terrorist incidents in Afghanistan and conveyed the message of condolences and sympathy from the Leader of the Islamic Revolution and the Islamic Republic to them. Muslims in neighboring Afghanistan witnessed deadly terrorist bombing attacks over the past few days during the holy months of Ramadan.